---
title: Sweet Chili Glazed Chicken Stuffed with Goat Cheese and Chives
description: Goat cheese stuffed chicken with a sweet chili glaze makes this weeknight meal feel like a date night. Green beans and roast potatoes round out this dinner! It's as easy as 1,2,3.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-chili-glazed-chicken-887f227e.jpg
